    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>tomato salsa</strong></p>",
