    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>pork mixture</strong> is cooked through, divide it evenly between your <strong>tortillas</strong>, covering half of the tortilla</p><p>Roll the <strong>tortillas</strong> tightly to form a cigar shape – these are your<strong> pork</strong> <strong>taquitos</strong></p>",
