    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>remaining smoked paprika </strong>in a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and a grind of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>paprika mayo</strong></p>",
